---
---
<section id="why-us" class="why-us">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="section-header text-center animate-fade">
			<span class="section-badge">Diferenciais</span>
			<h2>Por que escolher a Virada?</h2>
			<p>Oferecemos tudo o que o seu negócio precisa para crescer na internet.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="why-us-grid">
			<div class="glass-card why-card animate-fade" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
				<div class="icon-wrapper">
					<span class="icon">👥</span>
				</div>
				<h3>Mais Clientes</h3>
				<p>Um site profissional atrai mais clientes locais e converte visitantes em vendas reais.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="glass-card why-card animate-fade" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
				<div class="icon-wrapper">
					<span class="icon">🌐</span>
				</div>
				<h3>Presença Online</h3>
				<p>Apareça no Google e nas redes sociais. Seja encontrado pelos seus clientes quando procuram.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="glass-card why-card animate-fade" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
				<div class="icon-wrapper">
					<span class="icon">⭐</span>
				</div>
				<h3>Credibilidade</h3>
				<p>Transmita confiança com um design elegante e profissional que reflete a qualidade do seu negócio.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="glass-card why-card animate-fade" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
				<div class="icon-wrapper">
					<span class="icon">💰</span>
				</div>
				<h3>Custo Acessível</h3>
				<p>Planos simples e transparentes. Sem surpresas. Sem contratos longos. Apenas resultados.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.why-us {
		padding: 100px 0;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.section-header {
		margin-bottom: 60px;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.section-badge {
		color: var(--primary);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.section-header h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.section-header p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.why-us-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
		gap: 30px;
	}

	.why-card {
		padding: 40px 30px;
		text-align: center;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
		background: rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.4);
	}

	.why-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-10px);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
		border-color: var(--primary);
	}

	.icon-wrapper {
		width: 70px;
		height: 70px;
		background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		margin: 0 auto 20px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.why-card:hover .icon-wrapper {
		background: var(--primary);
		transform: scale(1.1);
	}
	
	.why-card:hover .icon {
		filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
	}

	.icon {
		font-size: 2rem;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.why-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.why-card p {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}
</style>
